OL,7,FA Muslim pupil has lost a High Court
OL,8,Fchallenge against a ban on prayer
OL,9,Frituals at a high-achieving north
OL,10,FLondon school previously dubbed
OL,11,FBritain's strictest.
OL,13,FThe student, who cannot be named, took
OL,14,Flegal action against Michaela
OL,15,FCommunity School in Brent, claiming
OL,16,Fthe policy was discriminatory and
OL,17,F"uniquely" affected her faith due to
OL,18,Fits ritualised nature.
