OL,7,FThe school's legal team told the court
OL,8,Fin London that students seen praying
OL,9,Foutside contributed to a "concerted
OL,10,Fcampaign" on social media over the
OL,11,Ffree school's approach to religion,
OL,12,Fwith there also being a since-removed
OL,13,Fonline petition attracting thousands
OL,14,Fof signatures.
OL,16,FThey added that the governors and
OL,17,Fheadteacher at the school of some 700
OL,18,Fpupils, about half of whom are Muslim,
OL,19,Fhad "a margin of latitude, discretion
OL,20,For judgment" over its policies.
