OL,7,FThe pupil's mother said she was
OL,8,F"profoundly dismayed by the case's
OL,9,Foutcome".
OL,11,FIn a comment issued by law firm
OL,12,FSimpson Millar, she said: "The case
OL,13,Fwas rooted in the understanding that
OL,14,Fprayer isn't just a desirable act for
OL,15,Fus - it's an essential element that
OL,16,Fshapes our lives as Muslims.
OL,18,F"In our faith, prayer holds undeniable
OL,19,Fimportance, guiding us through each
OL,20,Fchallenge with strength and faith."
